reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great case for a kid.
reviews.reviewText: This case provides the protection needed for a kids first phone. In my opinion, it's a bit too bulky and flashy for myself (or an adult in general), but for a kid it's perfect. It's easy to hold, there's a ton of all around protection, and the design/colors are fun. The built in finger hold is convenient and can be doubled as a kickstand to hold the phone up. It's a perfect fit for the A14 5G.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very durable. The option I LOVE is the camera lens has a side close case over it. Slide it to the left and it covers the lens, slide it to the right it opens and locks easy. Easily done with one hand. Fits snug. It's definitely a GO‼️📌

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I bought as gift but that person already had one.
reviews.reviewText: Well worth the money but that person already purchased one at Verizon, destroyed the box and couldn’t return. I really like how it was made, especially the cover on the picture view piece. Plus the cover locks in place. If I didn’t already have a cover, protector for my phone, I would definitely have kept this one. Color is great for guys too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Fits perfectly, excellent protection, ring stand is weak
reviews.reviewText: I'm not sure what other reviewers are talking about.... This fits the phone perfectly. If you have a different model then of course it's not going to fit perfectly. Also, you have to put BOTH parts on the phone--the flexible piece and the hard piece. One without the other will not work.The little ring stand in the back is VERY thin and flimsy. As long as you're careful when you rotate it, it should be fine. But I can easily see why it broke in other reviews. It needs to be redesigned.The sliding camera shield is fine. It's not too loose or tight, but I could see how it might be a source of problems in other reviews. I'm not sure how necessary it is, tbh.But the case seems pretty durable and protective. A little on the bulky side, like an Otter case. And the screen protector installed fine and doesn't seem to have affected the usage or appearance. I'd say this is a great buy. But be careful with the ring on the back!
